OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,FThe mother of a 23-year-old father who
OL,7,Fwas stabbed and killed has said he has
OL,8,Fhad "justice" after a man pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to his murder.
OL,11,FNewcastle man Bradley Tams was fatally
OL,12,Finjured by Gavin Train in Slatyford
OL,13,Flast December.
OL,15,FPolice were called to Cartmel Green
OL,16,Fjust before midnight on 6 December and
OL,17,Ffound Mr Tams had suffered serious
OL,18,Fstab injuries. He died at the scene.
