OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,FAn investigation revealed Mr Tams had
OL,7,Ftravelled to the address by taxi and
OL,8,Fwas followed by Train, who confronted
OL,9,Fhim about a previous dispute.
OL,11,FA physical and verbal altercation
OL,12,Fensued and Mr Tams fled the scene into
OL,13,Fa neighbouring block of flats after
OL,14,Fsuffering a single stab wound to his
OL,15,Fside.
OL,17,FTrain, 24, of Rothay Place, Newcastle,
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to murder during a
OL,19,Fhearing at Newcastle Crown Court on
OL,20,FFriday 7 June.
