OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,FLewis Allison, 24, of Roundhill
OL,7,FAvenue, Blakelaw, and Gavin's mother
OL,8,FAndrea Train, 49, of Rothay Place,
OL,9,FNewcastle, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,10,Fdisorder at the same hearing.
OL,12,FGavin Train was arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof murder shortly after the incident.
OL,15,FAll three have been remanded in
OL,16,Fcustody and are due to be sentenced
OL,17,Fnext month.
