OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,FFollowing the hearing, Julie
OL,7,FWeatherson, Bradley Tams' mother,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's the sixth month
OL,9,Fanniversary since the death of Bradley
OL,10,Fand today he's got the justice he
OL,11,Fdeserved"
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Katie Smith,
OL,14,Ffrom Northumbria Police, said: "First
OL,15,Fand foremost, I would like to thank
OL,16,FBradley's family and loved ones for
OL,17,Fthe incredible strength they have
OL,18,Fshown over the last six months since
OL,19,Fhis tragic passing.
