OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,F"Bradley was a beloved son, brother
OL,7,Fand father, and there is absolutely no
OL,8,Fjustification for the course of events
OL,9,Fwhich led to his death.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts very much continue to be
OL,12,Fwith them all, and I am pleased we
OL,13,Fhave been able to bring the person
OL,14,Fresponsible for his death to justice."
OL,16,FDet Ch Insp Smith added: "This case
OL,17,Fserves as yet another reminder that
OL,18,Fviolence destroys lives, and there is
OL,19,Fno place whatsoever for it in our
OL,20,Fcommunities.
