OL,3,C'Justice' for young dad after man
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to his murder
OL,6,F"As a force, we remain steadfast in
OL,7,Four resolve to reduce this type of
OL,8,Foffending through a range of tactics.
OL,10,F"The decision to carry a weapon that
OL,11,Fnight is the reason Bradley is no
OL,12,Flonger with us, and we have a very
OL,13,Fsimple message to those who carry
OL,14,Fknives and choose to involve
OL,15,Fthemselves in violence.
OL,17,F"Please think again ` not only for
OL,18,Fyour sake but for your family and
OL,19,Floved ones too."
